{"tid":1944160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國防部有海軍人員感染中國冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-03-26T08:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T08:15:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"384cdfb34178094ef0764f0113c89b5accb2afb9","tid":1944160,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"美國國防部有海軍人員感染新冠狀病毒<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍一名在國防部五角大樓上班的人員，確診感染新型冠狀病毒。國防部指，這名員工在家人出現病徵後，本月13日起已在家中自我隔離，他工作的地方已經消毒，部門並正追蹤他的接觸者。早前有兩名曾到五角大樓的國防部人員，亦證實染病。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國防部長埃斯珀下令所有美軍人員，未來60日要暫停前往海外，減少人員流動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276581&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276581%26csid%3D261_367&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=36c70350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276581&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"7a8f9ea45b8b6b9d76ea730efa12d1a673790583","tid":1944160,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"文職定軍人？"},{"pid":"f5e7f6d5fd5717354bac29aa148c826f27108380","tid":1944160,"uid":261339,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a8f9ea45b8b6b9d76ea730efa12d1a673790583","tid":1944160,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"文職定軍人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"文職啦，五角大樓d人又唔係史泰龍，日日對住部電腦打丁多過外勤"},{"pid":"fd1b13475e43f08582736ed66cd7af89fa0ebf98","tid":1944160,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"又比支那入位話病毒係美國製"},{"pid":"0ae1e934361a955ec2978c950c1263034ede13c9","tid":1944160,"uid":174060,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUdCPrx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=